Or just use Don's method.

Roll ATV jack under engine.
Raise jack until it lightly supports engine.
Unbolt engine.
Lift ATV jack a bit more.
Tug the engine loose.
Drop jack to lowest level.
Jack up bus and put on 2 jackstands.
Roll engine out.
Crack open favorite beverage.

